msg: This set of changes adds support for Google Gadgets where a locally-installed Shindig server is available. A stub method is supplied for registering Google Gadgets, invoked by:
In addition, the OpenSocial security token mechanism is supported with a very basic implementation. This still has issues and should be fixed in a future revision.
OpenSocial support is configured using the supplied opensocial.properties file.
